thread.title: MINDY

author: MINDY
title: MINDY
text:
First time using this service and my experience was effortless and cost effective from the time of booking the appointment to the completion of the service for both of our cars, the service guys were prompt and pleasant to deal with and happy with the outcome and it was convenient as they performed the service at my work place, job well done, to the boys at Lube Mobile.highly recommend the service.
Cheers Mindy D
